description:
Data repository for the Human Lung Development Atlas: 
 &nbsp; 
 Preprint: https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.09.24.678382 
 &nbsp; 
 Github: https://github.com/GreenleafLab/HLDA 
 &nbsp; 
 This repository contains compressed ArchR Projects 
 lda_v2.tar.gz = Combined ArchR Project of all cells in dataset. Includes both ATAC peak counts matrix and RNA features counts matrix. 
 Epithelial.tar.gz = Subclustered ArchR Project of all epithelial cells in dataset. Includes both ATAC peak counts matrix and RNA features counts matrix. 
 peaks.tar.gz = directory of peaks called from each cell type in BED format

